IssueTableResource only create columns for navigable fields.
The "Watched Issues" gadget call the IssueTableResource to retrieve all issues by the current user.
Since "watches" is not a navigable field, the result does not contain the total number of watchers, which is visible in the old "Watchs Issues" portlet.

